now: Why do humans have brains
the size they

52:30.948 --> 52:32.649 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
are?

52:32.750 --> 52:36.887 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
It's a mystery, but a new
mathematical model
may help scientists solve that
